data.description: Welcome to 241 Valley View Lane, Jacksonville, TX 75766! This charming brick home, situated on a solid slab foundation, boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, providing a cozy and comfortable living space within its approximate 1200 sq. ft. The residence is attractively priced to sell, making it an ideal opportunity for prospective homeowners.  Step inside to discover an open concept living/dining combo and galley style kitchen with range/oven, microwave and dishwasher. This property includes a garage, ensuring convenient parking and storage options. The central air and heat system (new in 2018) offers year-round comfort, creating a welcoming atmosphere for you and your family. Roof (new in 2019) is a 30 year composition shingle.  Enjoy the serenity of your surroundings in the privacy of your fenced backyard, complete with a covered patio. Whether you're entertaining guests or simply relaxing outdoors, this space offers the perfect retreat.  For added convenience, the home includes a utility room with washer/dryer hook-ups, streamlining your laundry routine.   Don't miss the chance to make this house your home. With its appealing features, affordable pricing, and desirable location, 241 Valley View Lane is a fantastic opportunity for those seeking a delightful living space in Jacksonville. Act fast, as this property is priced to sell and won't be on the market for long!
